    "name": "Hellknight Armiger",
    "type": "alien",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Hellknight armigers train under more experienced Hellknights until they succeed at the test that grants them the full rank of Hellknight. They have little to no leeway in interpreting their orders and strive to enforce all edicts given by their superiors.<br/><b>Adaptation:</b> A Hellknight armiger can function as an exceptionally disciplined Steward or bounty hunter. Alternatively, a Hellknight armiger could also be one of the soldiers of Castrovel's lashunta city-states."
        }
    ],
